en_528703_0	In order to prepare tri-service personnel of the Security Force Headquarters - Kilinochchi (SFHQ-KLN) to meet with any eventual disasters or emergency situations, a team of professionals held an awareness workshop on ‘Disaster Management’ for 571 Brigade troops of the 57 Division on Thursday (2) at the SFHQ-KLN auditorium.
en_528703_1	The full-day workshop, attended by a total of 45 service personnel learnt on ‘Recommended Practices in Emergencies of Floods and Droughts’ and received the support of the Disaster Management Centre (DMC).
en_528703_2	It received the blessings of the General Officer Commanding, 57 Division, Major General Vijitha Ravipriya.
en_528703_3	Assistant Director at Kilinochchi DMC, Mr S Epparajan delivered the lecture in this regard.
